.SH "NAME"
PAR::Filter::PodStrip \- POD\-stripping filter
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 2
\&    # transforms $code
\&    PAR::Filter::PodStrip\->apply(\e$code, $filename, $name);
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This filter strips away all \s-1POD\s0 sections, but preserves the original
file name and line numbers via the \f(CW\*(C`#line\*(C'\fR directive.
